FBIS3-35506 "drnes038_l_94018" FBIS-NES-94-038 Document Type:Daily Report 25 Feb 1994 ISRAEL Reaction From Various Leaders, Groups Noted Israeli Arabs, Druze Condemn Event TA2502121394 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 1100 GMT 25 Feb 94 TA2502121394 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] In the Israeli Arab community, all events planned for the Ramadan festival are being canceled. The Druze leadership held a special session this morning and sent out a cable denouncing the massacre in Hebron. Israeli Arab leaders have scheduled a special meeting this afternoon at Shefar'am.
